<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 22:06:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>数千人参加被杀的加拿大以色列和平活动家维维安·西尔弗的葬礼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/thousands-attend-funeral-of-slain-canadian-israeli-peace-activist-vivian-silver/0000018b-d9cd-d423-affb-fbef6e360000</link><description>以色列社会各界人士前来向西尔弗告别，西尔弗于 10 月 7 日在贝埃里基布兹的家中被哈马斯杀害。“你知道，我们说希伯来语还是阿拉伯语并不重要，这并不重要。”无论我们是出生在加沙边境还是加沙地带，你都知道我们的未来是紧密相连的。”和平活动家加迪尔·哈尼 (Ghadir Hani) 说道</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 21:38:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/thousands-attend-funeral-of-slain-canadian-israeli-peace-activist-vivian-silver/0000018b-d9cd-d423-affb-fbef6e360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布，在加沙 Al-Shifa 医院附近发现了 65 岁以色列人质尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/body-of-65-year-old-israeli-woman-hostage-found-near-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018b-d991-d168-a3ef-ddfb78ce0000</link><description>以色列士兵在大型医疗中心附近进行地面行动时发现了尸体，以色列国防军称哈马斯将其用作指挥中心</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 20:41:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/body-of-65-year-old-israeli-woman-hostage-found-near-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018b-d991-d168-a3ef-ddfb78ce0000</guid></item><item><title>绝食的以色列拉比：“人质没有接受红十字会探视，这太疯狂了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-rabbi-on-hunger-strike-insane-that-hostages-havent-received-a-red-cross-visit/0000018b-d8d0-df9a-ab8b-ded860090000</link><description>拉比阿维丹·弗里德曼现已绝食一周，呼吁以色列阻止人道主义援助进入加沙，直到红十字会获准接触被哈马斯扣押的 239 名以色列人质。他说：“人道主义援助需要面向全人类，我们的孩子也同样是人。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 20:39:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-rabbi-on-hunger-strike-insane-that-hostages-havent-received-a-red-cross-visit/0000018b-d8d0-df9a-ab8b-ded860090000</guid></item><item><title>从以色列国防军到孤立：以色列正统派如何应对哈马斯大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/from-idf-to-isolation-how-israels-haredim-are-responding-to-the-hamas-massacre/0000018b-d955-d423-affb-fbf787610000</link><description>该国现在有几个不同的极端正统派社区，其分歧不是由旧的宗教联系造成的，而是由每个群体的“以色列化”程度造成的</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 20:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/from-idf-to-isolation-how-israels-haredim-are-responding-to-the-hamas-massacre/0000018b-d955-d423-affb-fbf787610000</guid></item><item><title>为什么奥萨马·本·拉登在 TikTok 上走红？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-16/ty-article/.highlight/why-is-osama-bin-laden-going-viral-on-tiktok/0000018b-d94b-df9a-ab8b-dfcb3a530000</link><description>奥萨马·本·拉登 (Osama bin Laden) 在 TikTok 上很火爆，你可以责怪犹太人（就像他那样）</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 20:02:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-16/ty-article/.highlight/why-is-osama-bin-laden-going-viral-on-tiktok/0000018b-d94b-df9a-ab8b-dfcb3a530000</guid></item><item><title>有多少以色列人死亡？考古学家共同努力寻找人类遗骸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/archaeologists-assist-in-locating-human-remains-after-hamas-attacks/0000018b-d930-d168-a3ef-ddfa00260000</link><description>哈马斯的袭击造成了多少谋杀受害者、阵亡士兵、失踪人员和人质？一队考古学家来到加沙边境附近的基布兹尼尔奥兹，协助修复被烧毁的房屋</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 17:54:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/archaeologists-assist-in-locating-human-remains-after-hamas-attacks/0000018b-d930-d168-a3ef-ddfa00260000</guid></item><item><title>“自愿”驱逐加沙人：以色列立法者陷入煽动深渊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/voluntary-expulsion-of-gazans-the-israeli-lawmakers-falling-into-an-abyss-of-incitement/0000018b-d35b-d168-a3ef-d7fbc96c0000</link><description>摩萨德前副局长拉姆·本·巴拉克在《华尔街日报》上呼吁欧洲国家接收加沙难民，这只是种族清洗的美化版本，不负责任地瓦解了中间派和种族主义狂热分子之间的区别。以色列极右翼</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 16:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/voluntary-expulsion-of-gazans-the-israeli-lawmakers-falling-into-an-abyss-of-incitement/0000018b-d35b-d168-a3ef-d7fbc96c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布了在加沙地带遇难的另外三名士兵的姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-releases-names-of-three-additional-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-strip/0000018b-d8a5-d168-a3ef-ddff591c0000</link><description>以色列军队迄今公布了自10月7日与哈马斯开战以来阵亡的371名士兵的名字</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 16:04:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-releases-names-of-three-additional-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-strip/0000018b-d8a5-d168-a3ef-ddff591c0000</guid></item><item><title>长期被忽视且资金不足的以色列精神卫生系统无法治疗所有 10 月 7 日幸存者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/long-neglected-and-underfunded-israels-mental-health-system-unable-to-handle-survivors/0000018b-d4db-d168-a3ef-d5fb34660000</link><description>卫生部长表示，自战争爆发以来，约有10万人遭受过创伤性事件，而该系统还没有做好应对的准备。 “战争是全国性的心理健康事件”</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 15:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/long-neglected-and-underfunded-israels-mental-health-system-unable-to-handle-survivors/0000018b-d4db-d168-a3ef-d5fb34660000</guid></item><item><title>核掩体中的贾科梅蒂：10 月 7 日，以色列博物馆进入战时模式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-october-7-israels-museums-implemented-emergency-wartime-plans-to-save-their-art/0000018b-d867-df9a-ab8b-deeff65c0000</link><description>哈马斯渗透以色列后几个小时内，该国最大的博物馆紧急保护其最重要的物品，并将艺术品转入地下</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 15:10:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-october-7-israels-museums-implemented-emergency-wartime-plans-to-save-their-art/0000018b-d867-df9a-ab8b-deeff65c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙的战争不会削弱哈马斯的政治影响力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-in-gaza-wont-diminish-hamas-political-influence/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb12940000</link><description>哈马斯不仅仅是一个单纯通过军事行动就能消灭的恐怖组织。他们的金融和政治触角伸向世界各地，对以色列摧毁他们的承诺构成了重大障碍</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 15:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-in-gaza-wont-diminish-hamas-political-influence/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb12940000</guid></item><item><title>这位大屠杀幸存者希望招募纽约犹太人重建他的基布兹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/this-massacre-survivor-is-hoping-to-enlist-n-y-jews-in-rebuilding-his-kibbutz/0000018b-d80d-df9a-ab8b-decda9b00000</link><description>Or Yelin 正在纽约进行为期八天的筹款之旅，他希望为 10 月 7 日哈马斯暴行后遭受创伤的贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri) 成员筹集 1200 万美元</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 14:47:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/this-massacre-survivor-is-hoping-to-enlist-n-y-jews-in-rebuilding-his-kibbutz/0000018b-d80d-df9a-ab8b-decda9b00000</guid></item><item><title>与哈马斯的战争期间，以色列阿拉伯社区的凶杀率下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/homicide-rate-in-israels-arab-community-drops-during-war-with-hamas/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb38c50000</link><description>与 9 月份相比，谋杀案数量下降了 60%。专家将数量减少归因于更严格的执法，但警告称战争结束后数量将再次激增</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 14:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/homicide-rate-in-israels-arab-community-drops-during-war-with-hamas/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb38c50000</guid></item><item><title>南非政府是哈马斯和伊朗毫无歉意、无耻的代理人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/south-africas-government-is-an-unapologetic-shameless-proxy-for-hamas-and-iran/0000018b-d7d9-dffa-adef-f7d979970000</link><description>政府部长和哈马斯领导人之间的色情、阿谀奉承的恋情，对伊朗的热烈拥抱，明确呼吁攻击犹太人、我们的家园、我们的工作场所、我们的学校。我们南非犹太人想知道我们自己的政府是否正在煽动针对我们的大屠杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 13:51:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/south-africas-government-is-an-unapologetic-shameless-proxy-for-hamas-and-iran/0000018b-d7d9-dffa-adef-f7d979970000</guid></item><item><title>埃里温犹太教堂在亚美尼亚武装组织反犹太主义袭击中纵火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/yerevan-synagogue-set-on-fire-in-antisemitic-attack-by-armenian-militant-group/0000018b-d7ed-d423-affb-f7efb5d90000</link><description>据称，这次袭击是为了声援巴勒斯坦和黎巴嫩反对犹太复国主义的抵抗运动。该武装组织表示指责以色列支持阿塞拜疆，阿塞拜疆被指控对纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫的亚美尼亚人犯下战争罪</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 13:39:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/yerevan-synagogue-set-on-fire-in-antisemitic-attack-by-armenian-militant-group/0000018b-d7ed-d423-affb-f7efb5d90000</guid></item><item><title>拜登高级官员对约旦河西岸可能爆发另一条战线表示担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-officials-express-concern-about-possible-eruption-of-another-front-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-d79f-d423-affb-f7bf32040000</link><description>随着以色列继续对加沙进行地面入侵，美国官员担心约旦河西岸的相对平静可能很快演变成一场全面战争 — — 这是美国和以色列在政治上都无法承受的</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 13:05:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-officials-express-concern-about-possible-eruption-of-another-front-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-d79f-d423-affb-f7bf32040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯战争结束后，本·拉登为 9/11 所做的辩护在 TikTok 上疯传</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/bin-ladens-justification-for-9-11-goes-viral-on-tiktok-in-wake-of-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-d80f-df9a-ab8b-decf2c9c0000</link><description>这封信周三疯传后，《卫报》将其从网站上删除</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/bin-ladens-justification-for-9-11-goes-viral-on-tiktok-in-wake-of-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-d80f-df9a-ab8b-decf2c9c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的两国解决方案目前不可行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/a-two-state-solution-to-the-israel-palestine-conflict-is-currently-unviable/0000018b-d76b-dffa-adef-f76b885b0000</link><description>10月7日事件发生后，两国模式被视为幻想，同时也成为许多争论的话题。但在不久的将来的某个时刻，人们将会认识到当前的情况是不可持续的。那时这个想法将真正卷土重来。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:51:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/a-two-state-solution-to-the-israel-palestine-conflict-is-currently-unviable/0000018b-d76b-dffa-adef-f76b885b0000</guid></item><item><title>雷吉娜·斯佩克托：“许多像我一样的犹太人仍然处于震惊和悲伤之中”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/regina-spektor-many-jews-like-me-are-still-in-shock-and-sorrow/0000018b-d790-dffa-adef-f790f2900000</link><description>这位犹太裔美国歌手对 10 月 7 日之后反犹太主义的兴起感到惊讶，并发现自己从那时起就在社交媒体上争论不休。她对她的英雄尤其失望，其中包括冰岛音乐家比约克，他们对哈马斯的残酷袭击做出了反应。 “感觉就像喝下水道的水，”她告诉《国土报》</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:25:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/regina-spektor-many-jews-like-me-are-still-in-shock-and-sorrow/0000018b-d790-dffa-adef-f790f2900000</guid></item><item><title>自加沙战争爆发以来，进步民主党首次发起阻止美国向以色列出售武器的行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/progressive-democrats-launch-first-effort-to-block-arms-sales-to-israel-since-gaza-war/0000018b-d7be-d423-affb-f7bf71070000</link><description>众议员伊尔汗·奥马尔领导的反对决议呼吁阻止向以色列转让价值 3.2 亿美元的精确制导炸弹设备，因为以色列与哈马斯的战争已接近第七周</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:07:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/progressive-democrats-launch-first-effort-to-block-arms-sales-to-israel-since-gaza-war/0000018b-d7be-d423-affb-f7bf71070000</guid></item></channel></rss>